{"tid":1431603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【molamola】再咁做真係民意逆轉","createTime":"2019-08-08T04:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T04:40:56.000Z","uid":301166,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2d2a583e4e37dabf725735e076a5f457605e5fce","tid":1431603,"uid":301166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:37:56.000Z","msg":"我就由x月x日開始次次都有出去發夢嘅<br />\n[在此輸入一兩句顯得自己好多參與嘅事]<br />\n之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都堅持要尊重前綫決定<br />\n<br />\n我[屋企/朋友]好多本身都係淺藍，呢兩個月我用左好多心機去說服佢地支持我地，但上次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我真係唔知點同佢地解釋<br />\n<br />\n跪求大家唔好再<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，如果唔係民意真係會逆轉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌曬你地老母呀民意撚<br />\n成日提撚住做乜做勿會民意逆轉果啲自己咪就係會逆轉嘅民意囉</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前面啲手足拎條命出去搏都未出聲<br />\n你班民意撚俾身邊啲朋友話兩句就唔該屌撚住啦<br />\n諗唔到點同身邊啲人講咪上黎一齊諗囉<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">次次你諗唔到點同人解釋就叫前線唔好做</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁不如叫前線掛個牌係背脊解釋埋先好做啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你我地<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求一樣都未爭取到</span><br />\n點撚解要自我規範？<br />\n係咪規範左速龍會自爆？<br />\n係咪規範左林鄭會上吊？<br />\n係咪規範左習近平會讚你乖乖豬然後大大力錫你春袋？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">定係規範左就可以輸得好悽美呀？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">點都要講死都要講</span></span>"},{"pid":"35c4e69dafbcc85f1f4e4e6b72768a58e4855101","tid":1431603,"uid":245670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DmKk4Jh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDmKk4Jh.gif&h=3608e50d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}